Illana May (amụrụ n'onwa Febụwarị afọ 1976) bụ onye South Africa na-agụ egwu na-edekwa egwuma n'akpọkwa ụbọ
Ọ gụchara akwụkwọ na Messina, (nke a maara ugbu a dị ka Musina),na South Africa na Eric Louw High School
N'ihe karịrị ihe ngosi Mpụta ihe otu narị na iri asatọ kwa afọ, ọ bụ nwanyị na-eti egwu na South Africa
Site na CD asaa na DVD o wepụtara, ama egwu ya ama na Southern Africa.
Ka ọ na-eme ọtụtụ egwu mkpuchi, ọ na-emepụtakwa egwu mbụ ya na mmetụta rock dị iche iche
Ọ na-abụ abụ n'asụsụ Bekee na Afrikaans, ma na-eme egwu n'ụdị rock, pop, mba na ọdịda anyanwụ na R&B.
Na-ebi na Stage na Rustenburg, North West Province.
Live on Stage na Graceland Casino, Secunda, Mpumalanga Province
Live on Stage na Bela Bela, Limpopo Province
Na-ebi ndụ na Stage na Thabazimbi, n'ihu mmadụ 3000 Limpopo Province
